high_descs: Turn around and move to the right to face the sink.
Pick the soap up from off of the sink.
Move to the left to face the other sink.
Place the soap in to the sink, turn the water on, turn the water off, and pick up the soap.
Move to left to face the toilet.
Place the soap on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place the wet soap on top of the toilet next to the other soaps.

high_descs: Turn and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the soap from the sink.
Walk to the sink on the left.
Place the soap in the sink, turn the water on then off, then grab the soap.
Move in between the toilet and the left sink.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move a rinsed off bar of soap from the sink to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Go left, go forward, then turn left to face the rightmost sink.
Pick up the bar soap, on the counter, to the right of the sink.
Go left, then go forward, then go right to face the leftmost sink.
Wash the soap, in the sink.
Go to the toilet, next to the sink.
Put the bar soap on the back of the toilet, to the left of the hand soap.
anns.task_desc: Put a bar of soap on the back of the toilet.
